      • isForcedUnsolved

        public boolean isForcedUnsolved()
        Returns:
        true if this solution is triggered by a machine condition that absolutely needs to be addressed. This will force a solution to be unsolved, even is marked as "solved". Note, it will not force open a solution that is marked as "dismissed".
